EPA reserves the right to change information on EnviroFacts at any time without public notice. \n\nEPA uses the US Census Bureau 2014 tribal boundary layer data when developing environmental data query responses for tribes in the lower 48 United States and Bureau of Land Management Alaska State Office when developing environmental data query responses for tribes in Alaska.
